pageContext.claim: “We have claimed, for Electoral Vote purposes, the Commonwealth of Pennsylvania (which won't allow legal observers) the State of Georgia, and the State of North Carolina, each one of which has a BIG Trump lead. Additionally, we hereby claim the State of Michigan if, in fact, here was a large number of secretly dumped ballots as has been widely reported!”
pageContext.analysis: Trump has no right to claim states. The votes are counted and certified by individual states.
